10
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:07,776
Back in 1999.

11
00:01:07,859 --> 00:01:11,946
You couldn't even imagine
what's happening to me right now.

12
00:01:12,030 --> 00:01:14,199
Hello. Nam-gil.

13
00:01:14,282 --> 00:01:16,910
Are you insane?
You didn't like him yesterday,

