Get up.

95
00:06:48,533 --> 00:06:49,951
Why are you sleeping here?

96
00:06:50,034 --> 00:06:51,536
Why am I here?

97
00:07:02,004 --> 00:07:03,005
What is this?

98
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,882
What's wrong?

99
00:07:04,966 --> 00:07:07,135
-My gosh. Mom!
-What is it?

100
