next to a garbage can?

228
00:15:51,742 --> 00:15:54,078
-Go. Just go.
-What?

229
00:16:05,464 --> 00:16:07,174
-You may go.
-Salute.

230
00:16:15,182 --> 00:16:16,308
Darn it.

231
00:16:20,729 --> 00:16:21,897
